@startuml
title Observability - detail

skinparam componentStyle rectangle

[InferenceTelemetryRecorder] as InferenceTelemetry
[ResourceSampler] as ResourceSampler
[ObservabilityService] as ObservabilityApp
[ObservabilityRecorder] as Recorder
[ObservabilityWriter] as Writer
[RingEventStorage] as EventStorage
[InMemoryObservabilityState] as State
[Prometheus exporter] as Prometheus
[AutoRollbackMonitor] as RollbackMonitor
[WorkerRuntime] as WorkerRuntime

InferenceTelemetry --> Recorder
ResourceSampler --> WorkerRuntime
ResourceSampler --> Recorder

ObservabilityApp --> Recorder
ObservabilityApp --> Prometheus

Recorder --> Writer
Writer --> EventStorage
Writer --> State
Recorder --> State : query facade
Recorder --> RollbackMonitor : publishes events

note bottom of Recorder
  Public observability facade:
  records facts, keeps history query surface,
  and publishes events to subscribers.
end note

@enduml
